text: thumb | right|220px|Tusse Chiza in 2019 Tousin Michael Chiza (born 1 January 2002), better known as Tusse, is a Congolese-Swedish singer. He was in Talang 2018, the Swedish version of the Got Talent series. He represented Sweden in the Eurovision Song Contest 2021. ==References== ==Other websites== Category:Living people Category:2002 births Category:Swedish pop singers Category:Eurovision Song Contest entrants
